can you help test out this version: react-hook-form@4.9.3-beta.2

added type check.

```
import isObject from './isObject';
import { UNDEFINED } from '../constants';

export default (value: any): value is HTMLElement =>
  typeof Node !== UNDEFINED &&
  isObject(value) &&
  (value as any).nodeType === Node.ELEMENT_NODE;
```
